        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
        * renamed functions: arabic2romans -> arabit2roman, romans2arabic -> roman2arabic
        * doc
        
        0.1.0 (2015-03-22)
        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
